	• Flags for medical issues
		○ Physician places order
			§ System checks it
			§ Physician chooses whether or not to proceed.
	• Modality technician does not worry about approving flags.
		○ They just perform the procedure
	• Technician knows the steps and does not need prompts 
		○ Technician just has the options to perform the different procedures
		○ Takes picture
		○ Takes notes
		○ Patient appointment completed
		○ Info sent to database
	• Financial
		○ After procedure is completed the charge is captured
			§ After radiologist completes the report
		○ Bill patient directly, let him worry about every thing else
	• Referring physician is outside of scope
		○ Do not worry about him getting paid
 	• Prioritize requirements
		

		
